content.description: Stand start matched on crimp rail with a variety of foot options down low, pull on, and then either move right through several small crimps that trend up towards the lip or make a long reach to the lip. Match up on the lip and rock over to finish the climb.
content.location: On the left side of the Tree Wall, just below Warm-up Cave. Starting to the left of Eight Ball and just to the right of the tree against the wall.

content.description: Stand/squat start in the crack, trend up and right using good holds in the crack, moving up to a good edge at ~7/8', continue straight up through the small roof to good holds at the lip and topout right above the crack.
content.location: On the right side of the Tree Wall, just below Warm-up Cave. Starting under the small roof.

pathTokens: Warm Up Area aka The Tomato Overhangs / Mack'sTraverse

content.description: The Tree Wall sits just below Warm-Up Cave and has a few short and easy cracks; this is a good boulder to hit before getting on the harder stuff in the cave or if you wanted something less overhung.
